outputs.output_descr: UNDP will provide technical and policy advisory support through its direct engagement in the 11MP's Inter-Agency Planning Groups and Technical Working Groups and support the preparation of relevant Strategy Papers as inputs into the 11MP; organize related National Consultations and Focus Group Discussions around core issues to be addressed by the Plan; and organize relevant capacity building of EPU and line ministries as required in the preparation of the 11MP Report.

project_descr: Institutional Support For The Development Of The 11th Malaysia Plan: 2016-2020
